data.title: Manila RA - LET0318 - Social Studies - e PDF
data.meta_description: Manila RA_LET0318_Social Studies_e.pdf - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document is a list of examinees taking the Licensure Examination for Teachers - Secondary - Social Studies on March 25, 2018 at the FEU Institute of Technology in Manila. It includes the examinees' last name, first name, middle name, and school attended. There are instructions at the top for examinees to check for errors in their information and be punctual in reporting before 6:30am. The list continues on subsequent pages.
